reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Pretty, Lightweight Packing Cubes and Bags (5- Stars)
reviews.reviewText: As a frequent flier, I have come to rely on packing cubes to consolidate my clothes and make everything easy to find, but most cubes have solid, even utilitarian colors. These MissBoy cubes have a feminine, pink, floral pattern that makes them fun. The assortment of sizes and types is good -- the largest bag is the biggest I now own. Most have mesh sides for breathability and to make the contents easy to see, but one is solid for damp clothes. I love that there's a dedicated shoe bag and laundry bag. Still, these are NOT compression bags -- they don't have that extra zipper to squeeze out air. They compress simply by one bag pressing on another, and the air escaping through the mesh.These bags have two minor drawbacks: the nylon fabric is slippery, and the stitching looks like it might not last as long as some, especially after frequent, to-capacity use. The last is only a guess, though.I'm a sucker for packing cube sets, and I'm always looking for new looks and sizes. These MissBoy set makes a great addition to those I already own.-- Debbie Lee Wesselmann
